tips.text: Three hours on foursquare are as usual wrong.
This McDonald’s has free AT&T Wi-Fi. It’s easy to log on and stay connected while you dine.
Caramel frappe is a decent substitute since there is no Starbucks in Florence.
Cops are always outside so be cool if you come there drunk.
Eat the southern style chicken sandwich yummy :0)
This McDonald’s has free AT&T Wi-Fi. It’s easy to log on and stay connected while you dine.
Don't get the sausage mcmuffins. They can't toast them worth a crap. Chewy and off-putting.
Sausage Biscuit is on point when fresh but horrible when not.
